{"id":197278,"name":null,"username":"Echomote","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/echomote/{size}/161_2.png","created_at":"2004-10-16T13:17:04.000Z","cooked":"<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Gobbles\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"//forum.magicball.net/user_avatar/localhost/gobbles/48/218_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Gobbles:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Yes you are making a good point Bot13, couldnt you turn the perspective off too? then it would be genuenly isometric. And is there a way to actually control the camera during the game? like to get an Areal view of a whole island without moving Twinsen places?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>yeah. a whole camera controller would be brilliant.</p>","post_number":20,"post_type":1,"posts_count":23,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:06:40.834Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":19,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7611,"topic_slug":"an-all-isometric-lba2","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1083,"username":"Gobbles","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/gobbles/{size}/218_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"\n[quote=\"Gobbles\"]\nYes you are making a good point Bot13, could'nt you turn the perspective off too? then it would be genuenly isometric. And is there a way to actually control the camera during the game? like to get an Areal view of a whole island without moving Twinsen places?\n[/quote]\n\nyeah. a whole camera controller would be brilliant.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_